<br>
BAH is 40 48 w/ 4 magic damage and a 45 pt lifetap<br>
SSA is 33 / 36 8 sta 65 hp<br>
<br>
I'd be using them on a level 51 toon.  At what point would either one outdamage an Edge of Honor (20/24 1hs)?<br>
<br>
Thanks in advance for your feedback <p>---------------------<BR>
Dendrite, Grandmaster<BR>
